pyterLab interface. This provides an online,\nbrowser-based, near-native data analysis platform which supports user\ncomputation with fully local access to TNG data, alleviating the need to\ndownload large simulated datasets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Dec 2018 19:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 5 Apr 2019 12:52:26 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 29 Jan 2021 12:39:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-01"}
