oefficient) are vastly\ndifferent. \\color{black}\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Dec 2018 20:12:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 25 May 2019 22:34:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-24"}
