. We employ\nthese results to establish explicit relations between various types of\nquadrature rules from the above relations. A number of illustrative examples\nare provided.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 14 Dec 2018 11:26:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-07"}
